## Bug Report

The following test is generated by prop test and failed:
```
#[test]
fn test_case1() {
    let de = |data| {
        hex::decode(data).unwrap()
    };
    let cf = CF_WRITE;
    let operations = [
        Operation::Put(de("E2"), de("38CC98E09D9CB1D1")),
        Operation::DeleteRange(de("43AC4C5F7A16505B33EE3F"), de("E2")),
        Operation::Scan(de("2C0F698A"), 3),
    ];
    test_rocksdb_skiplist_basic_operations(cf, operations.to_vec());
}
```

The failed case was found by https://do.pingcap.net/jenkins/blue/organizations/jenkins/tikv%2Ftikv%2Fpull_unit_test/detail/pull_unit_test/1421/pipeline
